  "source_notes": "Originally this entry had a speculative time of 9pm (rated C) with Sy Scholfield quoting from \"Altonaer Nachrichten, \" 13 March 1896, p. 3: \"Stuttgart, 12. März. Die Herzogin Albrecht von Württemberg ist heute Abend von einem Prinzen entbunden worden\" (Stuttgart, 12 March. The Duchess Albrecht von Wurttemberg was this evening delivered of a prince).\\nOn 3 March 2017 Scholfield changed the time to 6:15pm (and the rating to A), having forwarded news report from \"Pester Lloyd,\" 13 March 1896, p. 3: \"Stuttgart, 12. März. Herzogin Margarethe Sophie von Württemberg, Gemahlin des Herzogs Albrecht von Württemberg, ist um 6¼ Uhr Abends von einem Prinzen glücklich entbunden worden.\" (Stuttgart, 12 March. Duchess Margarethe Sophie of Wurttemberg, wife of Duke Albrecht of Wurttemberg, was happily delivered of a prince at six-fifteen o'clock in the evening).\\n\\n\\n",
